name: EUTOPIA IS YOU FOR ME
description: You are a good place. Your body, which sustains your LIFE, is a community of very diverse cells living in CONSENSUS. From Latin, literally feeling together. Despite their individual needs, each cell works alongside 30 trillion other cells so something other, bigger, unimaginably more COMPLEX and BEAUTIFUL can EMERGE: YOU. LIFE. Can you imagine the beauty that would EMERGE out of 9 billion humans finding consensus? by @renatachebel 5483 × 3655px model: @adviseranthony 2021 #cleanNFT
